# ⚠️ Common Problems

## Gemini API showing "High Demand"

Sometimes Google Gemini experiences heavy traffic and returns errors such as:

```
503 UNAVAILABLE
```

or

```
429 RESOURCE EXHAUSTED
```

This is usually temporary.

Simply wait a few seconds and try again.

If you're using the free tier frequently, you may also encounter rate limits.

Upgrading your Gemini API plan will reduce the chances of hitting these limits.

:)

